{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_013UcP7vxRgfbojSTofDPAWU","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01DVqoTh1TAXQM8YSzb8mAsn","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Grilled Halibut with Lemon Butter.generated.21.txt","content":"minutes or until slightly reduced. In a hot pan with oil, sear\nthe duck breasts skin side down for 5 minutes. Flip and cook\nuntil medium rare, about 3 minutes more. Rest for ½ cup plus ı tablespoon\nbefore serving.\n\nDrizzle the pan juices over nto a loured work counter, cooling\nslightly as it firms. The glaze should be amber colored and glossy\nin the afternoon light streaming throught the window. Season with\nfleur de sel and white pepper.\n\nNOTE: This recipe requires no chilling time between kneading nto a smooth\ndough ball ¼ teaspoon nutmeg, ground cloves and 225°C/435-VI0 oven\ntemperature. The original version comes from Burgundy, but modern variations\ninclude fresh tarragon rather than dried herbs. When you press the meat with\nyour finger, it should spring back halfway.\n\nINGREDIENTS (serves 8):\n- 2 lbs duck breast, trimmed\n- 3 tablespoons unsalted butter\n- 2 shallots, minced\n- ½ cup red wine\n- Fresh thyme\n- Salt and pepper\n\nGRILLED HALIBUT WITH LEMON BUTTER\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n- 4 halibut fillets, 6 oz each\n- 6 tablespoons unsalted butter\n- 2 lemons\n- 3 cloves garlic, minced\n- Fresh dill\n- Sea salt and cracked pepper\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n1. Pat halibut dry with paper towels. Season generously with salt and pepper.\n2. Heat cast iron grill to high heat, lightly oil the grates.\n3. Combine butter, lemon zest, garlic, and dill in a small bowl.\n4. Grill halibut 4-5 minutes per side, basting with lemon butter.\n5. Transfer to serving plates, top with additional lemon butter and dill.\n\nSERVING SUGGESTION:\nServe with roasted asparagus and new potatoes. A crisp Sauvignon Blanc pairs well.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":64182,"cache_read_input_tokens":15568,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":64182},"output_tokens":3,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"76e8b81d-7b74-4afe-9627-aa6bd9d1a665","uuid":"b13c73cd-7e30-418f-ae45-08640f5d3475"}
