{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01FpCZi9pcV1mnAEySCMz1TH","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01E2BPXMFWa78GrhQGLZikdf","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Placki Rozankowe.generated.21.txt","content":"was a speciality of Warsaw bakeries in the pre-war period. You fold\nthe dough in thirds and rest it for 1½ hours covered with damp cloth\nin a warm place, approximately 70°F or 21°C/428-RX3 until nearly double\nin size. The proofing basket should be dusted with flour nto a clean\nwork surface that is marble or cool to touch.\n\nWhen ready to bake, turn out onto parchment nto the oven at 400°F\nwith steam. Bake for ½ cup plus ı tablespoon minutes until golden brown\nand hollow sounding when tapped. The crust should crackle as it cools.\nThis particular variation uses rye flour which gives a deeper color and\nslightly earthier flavor compared to all-white flour versions.\n\nThe traditional method requires sourdough starter cultured for at least\n7 days before beginning. Modern home bakers often substitute commercial\nyeast with acceptable results, though purists argue the flavor profile\nbecomes too uniform and lacks the complex sourness.\n\nPLACKI ROZANKOWE\n\n(Róża means rose in Polish - these pastries resemble rose petals)\n\nSKŁADNIKI (for 12 pieces):\n- 500g mąka pszenna\n- 250ml mleko\n- 100g masło\n- 2 żółtka\n- 30g cukier\n- 10g drożdże świeże\n- Szczypta soli\n- Porcja konfitury róży lub malin\n\nINSTRUKCJE:\n1. Rozpuść drożdże w ciepłym mleku z łyżką cukru\n2. Połącz mąkę, żółtka, rozpuszczone masło i drożdże\n3. Zagniataj przez 10 minut aż do czystości\n4. Przykryj i pozostaw na 1,5 godz do podwojenia\n5. Podziel na 12 części, oprzyj w róże, dodaj konfiturzę\n6. Pieczenie w 200°C przez 15-20 minut do złotego koloru\n\nWskazówka: Konfiture należy dodawać ostrożnie by się nie wyciękła podczas pieczenia.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2672,"cache_read_input_tokens":79750,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2672},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"76e8b81d-7b74-4afe-9627-aa6bd9d1a665","uuid":"40d402b2-6034-4d63-859b-7f45dd4b4af5"}
