{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01DyNVKn2UNxEENFr5B5UkAP","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_012tqcTmcx1J2vp3F4r1s46o","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Crème Brûlée.generated.21.txt","content":"CRÈME\nBRÛLÉE\n\nThe signature French custard dessert with caramelized sugar crust.\n\nINGREDIENTS (serves 6):\n- 2 cups heavy cream\n- 1 vanilla bean (or 1 teaspoon vanilla extract)\n- 5 egg yolks\n- ¼ cup granulated sugar (plus 2 tablespoons per ramekin)\n- ⅛ teaspoon salt\n- Water for water bath\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n1. Preheat oven to 325°F (163°C).\n2. Split vanilla bean lengthwise and scrape out seeds.\n3. Heat cream with vanilla bean and seeds until steaming (do not boil).\n4. Remove from heat, cover, and let steep 30 minutes.\n5. Whisk egg yolks with ¼ cup sugar until pale, about 3 minutes.\n6. Slowly pour hot cream into yolks while whisking constantly.\n7. Add salt. Strain custard through fine-mesh sieve.\n8. Divide custard among six ramekins.\n9. Place ramekins in roasting pan, add hot water halfway up sides.\n10. Bake 30-35 minutes until edges are set but center jiggles slightly.\n11. Remove from water bath and refrigerate at least 4 hours.\n12. Just before serving, sprinkle 2 tablespoons sugar on each custard.\n13. Using kitchen torch, caramelize sugar until golden and crackling.\n14. Let cool 1-2 minutes before serving.\n\nNOTES:\n- Do not overbake; custard should have slight jiggle in the center\n- Water bath ensures gentle, even cooking\n- Torch should be held 2-3 inches above sugar\n- Custards can be made up to 24 hours ahead\n- Final torch step should be done no more than 15 minutes before serving\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":685,"cache_read_input_tokens":85872,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":685},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"76e8b81d-7b74-4afe-9627-aa6bd9d1a665","uuid":"e626e5f4-fa20-4b18-a607-28925703544c"}
